nodes.bodyText:
Might be personal opinion, but I feel like it might be easier to understand what's happening in this method if you explicitly spell out what types are allowed to move into a parent type, so maybe a static variable something like:
allowedMoveMappings = { 
       'AdminUnit' : ['Collection'],
       'Collection' : ['Folder', 'Work'],
       ...};

current implementation feels a bit opaque/magical to me.

